original: intros H. unfold Rbar_le. destruct H as [x Hx]. destruct (Rbar_ex_glb E) as [glb Hglb]. assert (HglbE: Rbar_is_lower_bound E (proj1_sig glb)). { destruct Hglb. apply i. } apply HglbE in Hx. destruct (Rbar_ex_lub E) as [lub Hlub]. assert (HlubE: Rbar_is_upper_bound E (proj1_sig lub)). { destruct Hlub. apply i. } apply HlubE.
